---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 344-345
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
By: Tauler
---
For so long as a man is not standing in the grace of God, he is
standing alone in nature.  And if such a man (were it possible, which
it is not) were to fulfil all the good works which have ever been done
in this world, he would still, nevertheless, be living altogether
idly, unprofitably, and in vain, and it would avail him nothing.
